{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_CFlamePuff}}
'''A_CFlamePuff'''

(no parameters)

Removes the {{Flag|INVISIBLE}} flag, stops the calling actor, and plays the sound ClericFlameExplode on the BODY channel.

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|CFlameMissile}} and actors inheriting from it.

